### API HTTP request tests for categories, allergens endpoints

### Categories

### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories

### Get category by ID (Snacks)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/1

### Get category by ID (Mains)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/2

### Get category by ID (Desserts)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/3


### Get category by ID (Drinks)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/4




### Allergens

### Get all allergens
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/allergens

### Get allergen by ID (Lactose-free)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/allergens/1


### Get allergen by ID (Gluten-free)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/allergens/2


### Get allergen by ID (Dairy-free)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/allergens/3


### Get allergen by ID (Vegan)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/allergens/4


### Get allergens for menu item
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/allergens/menu-item/8




### Lunch Specials

### Get all lunch specials
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/lunch

### Get today's lunch special
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/lunch/today


### Get lunch for specific day
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/lunch/tuesday

